---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Responsible Use | Mount Kush Cannabis Lifestyle Store" description="Mount Kush Responsible Use Disclaimer. Cannabis is for adults 18+. Use responsibly. South African law compliance." noIndex={false}>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Responsible Use</div>
      <h1 class="display-md">Use Responsibly</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:1rem;">Mount Kush is committed to responsible adult cannabis use. We take this seriously.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--purple-deep);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">

        <div class="warning-box">
          <strong style="color:white; font-size:1.05rem;">🔞 Adults Only — 18 Years and Older</strong><br/><br/>
          Cannabis products and accessories are sold exclusively to adults 18 years of age and older. Mount Kush strictly enforces this policy. Age verification may be required in-store.
        </div>

        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush promotes responsible, informed, and legal cannabis use among consenting adults. We believe in cannabis as a lifestyle choice that deserves respect — from the people who use it and the businesses that serve them.</p>
        <p>We do not promote excessive use, underage use, or any unsafe behaviour involving cannabis or cannabis accessories.</p>

        <h2>South African Law</h2>
        <p>The Constitutional Court of South Africa confirmed in September 2018 (<em>Minister of Justice and Constitutional Development and Others v Prince</em>) that adults have the right to use, possess and cultivate cannabis privately for personal consumption.</p>
        <p>The Cannabis for Private Purposes Act, 2024 further decriminalised private adult use. However, the sale, supply or trade in cannabis remains regulated. Mount Kush operates strictly within applicable South African law and sells accessories and lifestyle products to adults.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:var(--gold-bright);">Important:</strong> Mount Kush sells cannabis <strong style="color:white;">accessories</strong>, <strong style="color:white;">lifestyle gear</strong> and <strong style="color:white;">branded merchandise</strong> only. We do not sell cannabis flower, edibles, concentrates or any controlled substance.
        </div>

        <h2>Responsible Use Guidelines</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Do not drive</strong> under the influence of cannabis. Impaired driving is illegal and dangerous.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Keep cannabis away from children</strong> and minors at all times.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Use in private spaces</strong> — public cannabis use remains an offence under South African law.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Be mindful of others</strong> who may not wish to be exposed to cannabis smoke.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Know your limits</strong> — cannabis affects individuals differently. Start low, go slow.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Do not mix</strong> cannabis with alcohol or other substances without understanding the effects.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Avoid use during pregnancy</strong> or while breastfeeding.</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">If you have a medical condition</strong> or take medication, consult a doctor before using cannabis.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Mental Health</h2>
        <p>Cannabis use may have different effects on individuals with certain mental health conditions. If you have a personal or family history of psychosis, schizophrenia or anxiety disorders, we recommend consulting a healthcare professional before use.</p>
        <p>If you or someone you know is struggling with substance dependency, please seek professional help.</p>

        <h2>Support Resources</h2>
        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:white;">SADAG — South African Depression and Anxiety Group</strong><br/>
          0800 21 22 23 (free helpline)<br/>
          <a href="https://www.sadag.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--gold-bright);">www.sadag.org</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Our Promise</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush will not sell to anyone who appears to be a minor. We will not knowingly facilitate unsafe, irresponsible or illegal use. We are part of the Johannesburg community and we take that responsibility seriously.</p>
        <p>High on Healing means healing — not harm.</p>

        <p style="margin-top:3rem; font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">For queries contact us on WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/27639260217" style="color:var(--gold-bright);">063 926 0217</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
